### Context

Hey folks, 
Two days ago, I decided to work with a **Walmart dataset**. Like predict something or visualize something by dataset of Walmart. So this dataset I think the same I wanna work with. Guys give support and do some notebooks so that I will know many techniques of visualization and Analyzation.
 

### Content

The Data set contains three csv files :

* walmart.csv
* walmartSample.csv

### Inspiration

Dataset is inspired or Source is https://data.world/
There is one more dataset on Kaggle which tells about the same but this is the updated version of that dataset.
